{"tid":453640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰隆尼亞違法獨立 恐成歐洲孤兒〈蕭若元：海外蕭析〉","createTime":"2017-10-31T11:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T12:47:19.000Z","uid":49391,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00f8729090476381819c5a47727439a5a229329f","tid":453640,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TrioFrvF6bI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTrioFrvF6bI&d=NmQg4hzuelNsIzkRmOffeMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=fe9e6692\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TrioFrvF6bI</a>"},{"pid":"ddadcbcf8da5dad9bc18cbbddbeb8318efbcc222","tid":453640,"uid":14719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32d43fc18737077b93742c08c365b9cfbd710d0","tid":453640,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"燒山加持<br />\n今次有救啦"},{"pid":"178ff7ac1eebb8fee8fd2aff151a227032c31d84","tid":453640,"uid":59901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"加泰有救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624653171ddd703ac345a885547a9dbcddd184c3","tid":453640,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山"},{"pid":"0e33b29e4c0c13089b73f4c396e55bfbd4e39a82","tid":453640,"uid":57705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6764fcc66f5988dda5c207839e3306a4cc3ab77","tid":453640,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"加獨之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e6d767173e630cfc88a7c5c941a1778471ec1d","tid":453640,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"加獨要感恩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cf67527e67811f4f25134bf36cbfc1144c5521","tid":453640,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:22:54.000Z","msg":"加獨最後一塊拼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6b52c23f50b3561e0024732ebaa2155f3e838d","tid":453640,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"早年經歷<br />\n蕭若元於1966年中學會考，成績有三優四良，是班中之冠，其中中國歷史、中文和英國文學均獲「A」。其後他續升讀預科時，他的中七高級程度會考成績，以四科良入讀香港大學歷史系。<br />\n<br />\n成年經歷<br />\n畢業於聖保羅書院、香港大學歷史系，修讀港大歷史系碩士時輟學。曾於股票經紀行大和證券任職出市代表。蕭為人靈活多計，獲員工譽為「蕭才子」，近亦通稱「知名網民」。<br />\n1973年香港股災後，為了出名做生意容易而進入無線電視，有過一段試做遊戲節目，後被叫去見何掌邦，便任晚間新聞報導員。<br />\n<br />\n1976年4月16日，無線電視與麗的電視同日推出早晨新聞不久便與英文台的John Culkiin一同主持麗的晨早新聞。其後受黃錫照及麥當雄賞識，同時參與電視劇創作，在麗的電視編寫了很多著名長篇電視劇約20套電視劇，當中包括《鱷魚淚》、《浮生六劫》、《天蠶變》及《大地恩情》等長編劇集。<br />\n<br />\n1970年代末至1980年代初，與麥當雄一同主政麗的電視，任節目策劃經理。<br />\n<br />\n1981年7月與麥當雄一同離開麗的，改投電影製作。同時與其家族經營建材公司友聯建築材料，後來成功於香港上市。<br />\n<br />\n1987年至1988年，受黃玉郎邀請，在玉郎集團參與《醉拳》及《龍虎門》等暢銷漫畫之編劇工作。<br />\n<br />\n1991年，以電影《跛豪》獲「香港電影金像獎」最佳劇本。"},{"pid":"97c918efd4c335314cc7456c60a8182ed0ff5985","tid":453640,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"God bless cata"},{"pid":"b5d6288f3ab7855536d81e140f39d995422bd05c","tid":453640,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝燒山</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字試用版</ins><br />\n<br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=